Module it.polimi.ingsw
Package it.polimi.ingsw.model

Class Player

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.Player
public class Player
extends java.lang.Object
The class representing a player, which can choose a god and has a list of workers that can do actions during his turn. The player is identified by his nickname and age
